    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit showcases exceptional mechanical health, with the double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies operating in perfect synchronicity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, feeding power through a factory limited-slip differential. Preventative maintenance is comprehensive, including documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The exterior retains its original deep luster with no signs of panel fatigue, while the interior remains free of bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically superlative example for the discerning collector.",
