    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections here. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic feature, from the premium surround-sound system to the high-resolution navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak form, having been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized centers with a full log of records provided. The engine bay is immaculate, reflecting the same level of care as the rest of the vehicle. This is a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like it just left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
