    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new adventure. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just left the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it's completely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one. Come by and see it for yourself; I promise you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
