    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, a benchmark in longitudinal FR layout precision. Powered by the F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC engine, this unit exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders and retains its signature 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is corroborated by original VIN stamps on all panels and a pristine undercarriage. Featuring the OEM close-ratio six-speed gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, the drivetrain provides immediate engagement and tactile feedback. This example is free of any aftermarket modifications, preserving the factory-tuned double-wishbone suspension and aerodynamic balance. A rare, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
